'''Botswana''' ke [[naga]] [[lefasana|lefasaneng]] la [[Afrika]]. ''Botswana'' e borwa bja Afrika, e wela seleteng sa [[Borwa bja Afrika|Borwa Bja Afrika]].

''Botswana'' e agišane le :
* [[Afrika Borwa]] (borwa le go ya borwa bohlabela),
* [[Namibia]] (bodikela),
* [[Zambia]] (leboa) le
* [[Zimbabwe]] (leboabo hlabela).

''Botswana'' ke e tee ya dinaga tša Afrika, yeo [[landlocked|e sa bapago]] le [[lewatle]].

